Updated to multi-targeted NetStandard1.3 &amp; NetFramework4.6.</PackageReleaseNotes>
    <PackageProjectUrl>https://github.com/gregsdennis/Manatee.Trello</PackageProjectUrl>
    <PackageLicenseUrl>https://github.com/gregsdennis/Manatee.Trello/blob/master/LICENSE.txt</PackageLicenseUrl>
    <PackageIconUrl>https://bytebucket.org/gregsdennis/manatee.trello/wiki/Resources/Manatee-Trello-ManateeJson-Icon.png</PackageIconUrl>
